data.description: 4809 Jessica Lane is located in the Rocky Run neighborhood in Castle Hayne with spacious lots, mature trees, pleasing architecture and no through traffic. Built in 1998, the home blends classic and modern features, and the single-level design makes it convenient and accessible, with no stairs to navigate. The home has a spacious primary bedroom with en suite bathroom and two other bedrooms and a second full bathroom. Great layout with a spacious family room, updated kitchen with an eat in kitchen area, and a large dining area.  This home is loaded with features including laminate floors, new carpet, gas logs fireplace, upgraded cabinets, granite counter tops, stainless appliances, wainscoting, HVAC system new in 2020, crawlspace encapsulated and dehumidified in 2023, big deck on the back and covered front porch on the front complete with your own porch swing. The quiet street enhances the tranquility of the area, and the covered front porch is an inviting space to relax and enjoy the surroundings. Despite its proximity to town, the property offers a countryside ambiance creating a remote and peaceful atmosphere. The back yard is also fully fenced. The absence of homeowner association (HOA) dues and city taxes is a significant cost-saving and the property is ready for immediate occupancy. Fridge, washer and dryer included!
